            <thetext>There should be a minimal schema check when a config file is read, to warn 
about unknown keys, or keys having the wrong value type.

Solving this issue does not withstand implementing a more formal schema check 
for config files (e.g. using json schema).</thetext>
          </long_desc>
          <long_desc isprivate="0">
