            <who name="Thomas Herchenroeder">thron7</who>
            <bug_when>2010-08-10 13:40:17 +0200</bug_when>
            <thetext>Implemented .checkSchema() methods for Config and Job classes. A simple check 
is done when a config file is loaded, checking for unknown top-level and 
job-level keys. When all jobs are expanded, another check run is made, looking 
at the values of job-level keys (only basic checks for Dict, List, etc.).

With r22997.</thetext>
